Object.Field: OdiSqlUnload "-FILE=#GLOBAL.V_ATTACHMENT" "-DRIVER=#GLOBAL.V_JDBC_DRIVER" "-URL=#GLOBAL.V_JDBC_URL" "-USER=#GLOBAL.V_USER" "-PASS=#GLOBAL.V_PASS" "-FILE_FORMAT=VARIABLE" "-ROW_SEP=\r\n" "-DATE_FORMAT=yyyy/MM/dd" "-TIME_FORMAT=HH:mm:ss" "-CHARSET_ENCODING=ISO8859_1" "-XML_CHARSET_ENCODING=ISO-8859-1" with odi_log as (select 0 line_no, rpad('ODI Load Plan ID',16) as col1, rpad('ODI Load Plan Name',50) as col2, rpad('ODI Session ID',30) as col3, rpad('Scenario Name',150) as col4, rpad('Scenario Version',5) as col5, rpad('Target Table Name',50) as col6, rpad('Last Execution Date',20) as col7, rpad('Execution Duraction',10) as col8, rpad('Execution Status',20) as col9, rpad('File Name',200) as col10 from dual union select rownum as line_no, rpad(to_char(a.LOAD_ID),16) as "ODI Load Plan ID", rpad('<%=odiRef.getLoadPlanInstance("LOAD_PLAN_NAME")%>',50) as "ODI Load Plan Name", /*rpad('ABC_LP',50) as "ODI Load Plan Name",*/ rpad(to_char(a.ETL_RUN_WID),30) as "ODI Session ID", rpad(a.SCENARIO_NAME ,150)as "Scenario Name", rpad(to_char(a.SCENARIO_VERSION),5) as "Scenario Version", rpad(a.TARGET_TABLE_NAME,50) as "Target Table Name", rpad(to_char(a.LAST_EXECUTION_DT,'dd-mm-rrrr'),20) as "Last Execution Date", rpad(to_char(b.EXECUTION_DURATION),10) as "Execution Duraction", rpad(a.RUN_STATUS,20) as "Execution Status165", rpad(NVL(b.ATTRIBUTE1,'N/A'),200) as "File Name" from <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("DW_ADW", "D")%>.w_etl_load_dt a, <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("DW_ADW", "D")%>.w_etl_load_his_dtl b where a.ETL_RUN_WID = b.ETL_RUN_WID and a.RUN_STATUS = 'Success' and a.LOAD_ID = #GLOBAL.V_LOAD_PLAN_ID order by 1 asc) select col1,col2,col3,col4,col5,col6,col7,col8,col9,col10 from odi_log
